{"article_id":"hNqKP2XnAfXBxD6b","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump had a lot of topics","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to cover outside the White House ahead of his trip to New Orleans Monday .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Namely , how the Washington impasse over border security has now kept the government shuttered for 24 days .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"supports the president 's plan","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to construct a wall along the U.S.-Mexico border ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"even to the point","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"where he urged him to declare a national emergency","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"if the Democrats do n't budge .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Build a wall NOW .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"- Lindsey Graham","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"( @ LindseyGrahamSC )","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"January 11 , 2019","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"However , Graham recently suggested","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Trump consider a stopgap spending bill","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that would reopen the government for three weeks","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"and give them more time","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to talk with Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"But on Monday Trump confirmed","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"he rejected it .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" I ' m not interested , ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"`` I want to get it solved .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"I don ' t want to just delay it .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"I want to get it solved . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"The president also continued to sound off on Democrats","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"who flew to Puerto Rico","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"instead of staying in Washington","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to find a solution .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"He 's been tweeting all weekend","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"how he has been waiting in the White House","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"for Democrats to show up at his door .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Judging by the sheer volume of his tweets ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"he 's getting bored .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Wish","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"I could share with everyone the beauty and majesty","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"of being in the White House","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"and looking outside at the snow filled lawns and Rose Garden .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Really is something","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"- SPECIAL COUNTRY , SPECIAL PLACE !","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"January 13 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"If they really wanted to ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"they could end the shutdown in 15 minutes .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Instead ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"he noted on Monday ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"they 're in Puerto Rico","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"`` celebrating . '","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"' Maybe ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"they 're `` celebrating the shutdown . ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Chuck Schumer and Nancy Pelosi are not negotiating in good faith with @ realDonaldTrump .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Instead , Congressional Democrats spent the weekend on the beach with lobbyists .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"It ' s time for them to get back to Washington","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and work","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to secure our border","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"and reopen the government .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"- Ronna McDaniel","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"( @ GOPChairwoman )","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"January 13 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Kellyanne Conway also shamed the Democrats ' travel plans .","depth":3},{"id":64,"text":"`` I know","de